\{row(2, $p2)\}
\{row(3, $p3)\}
\{row(4, ans_rule(20))\}
\{row(5, $p5)\}
\{endtable()\}
END_TEXT
}

BEGIN_TEXT 

Would it be unusual to roll a pair of dice \( 5 \) times and get no \( $a \)s? $BR
(enter YES or NO) \( \ \) \{ans_rule(10)\}

END_TEXT

ANS(num_cmp($ans));
ANS(str_cmp($ans2));

